1. untar acti_x.x.x.tar.gz and mv files to $HOME/.acti/ or elsewhere
2. gzip acti.1 and cp it to /usr/share/man/man1/acti.1
3. configure parameters in acti.config (see file in dir ./examples)
4. set $config_file in acti (line 3)
5. make acti executable and cp it to /usr/local/bin or $HOME/bin
6. set dir ./utils in acti.config and scripts in that dir executable
7. if you like it, configure a shortcut that executes acti (for example win+v)
8. create your app file and insert minimum one app
9. then go
